## Examples

### Internal Disk

```terraform
resource "cloudavenue_vm_disk" "example-internal" {
	vapp_id = cloudavenue_vapp.example.id
	name = "disk-example-internal"
	bus_type = "NVME"
	size_in_mb = 104800
	is_detachable = false
	vm_id = cloudavenue_vm.example.id
}
```

### External Disk

